  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Us on Discord!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/4661d0a67d32825967b8d37d05b4794a.poster.avif?t=1738003798\" width=614 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/4661d0a67d32825967b8d37d05b4794a.webm?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/4661d0a67d32825967b8d37d05b4794a.mp4?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The <strong><i>A.V.A.F</i></strong> (anti-vandal-attack-force) is planning to wipe away the graffiti that coats the city streets. This municipal force won't hesitate to flush out any filth, along with your new crew. <strong>It's time to make a mess.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/aea9b6334e739b7c29e49f1f19b99e56.poster.avif?t=1738003798\" width=614 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/aea9b6334e739b7c29e49f1f19b99e56.webm?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/aea9b6334e739b7c29e49f1f19b99e56.mp4?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>TAGLINE is a lightning fast <strong><i>graffiti-based platformer</i></strong> with a unique weapon swapping mechanic: Switch powers on the fly by snatching tags off the walls of a funky-futurist metropolis!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/f94e5feadbba322b37e64016dd083d1a.avif?t=1738003798\" width=615 height=129 /></span><br>Help a cast of <strong><i>hand animated characters</i></strong> fight back against the A.V.A.F by taking on challenges across open level city districts. Compete assorted score based challenges to prove yourself and upgrade your skills!  <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A retro FPS with a new style:</strong> Funky 2D animations and particles clash with an oppressive 3D world, while deep mechanics and fluid movement bring a fresh feel to the genre.<br></li><li><strong>No nonsense gameplay:</strong> Quick switch powers on the fly without worrying about ammo, simple controls mean TAGLINE is easy to learn and difficult to master! <br></li><li><strong>The Sky is the Limit:</strong> Progress through a handcrafted world featuring open playgrounds, each with their own missions and secrets to discover!<br></li><li><strong>5 powerful skills:</strong> Ride explosions, scale buildings, and fly through the air with 5 unique abilities. Each with their own upgrades, dynamic uses, and synergies!<br></li><li><strong>Fill your black book:</strong> Hunt down 100+ unique graffiti designs and chronicle the history of the TAGGERS, a group of street artists lost to time.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/07067e475da74062b7753d86ef766454.poster.avif?t=1738003798\" width=614 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/07067e475da74062b7753d86ef766454.webm?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/07067e475da74062b7753d86ef766454.mp4?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/771c476f45f005cfa4252b7f090c1e22.webp?t=1738003798\" width=600 height=57 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/4661d0a67d32825967b8d37d05b4794a.poster.avif?t=1738003798\" width=614 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/4661d0a67d32825967b8d37d05b4794a.webm?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/4661d0a67d32825967b8d37d05b4794a.mp4?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The <strong><i>A.V.A.F</i></strong> (anti-vandal-attack-force) is planning to wipe away the graffiti that coats the city streets. This municipal force won't hesitate to flush out any filth, along with your new crew. <strong>It's time to make a mess.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/aea9b6334e739b7c29e49f1f19b99e56.poster.avif?t=1738003798\" width=614 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/aea9b6334e739b7c29e49f1f19b99e56.webm?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/aea9b6334e739b7c29e49f1f19b99e56.mp4?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>TAGLINE is a lightning fast <strong><i>graffiti-based platformer</i></strong> with a unique weapon swapping mechanic: Switch powers on the fly by snatching tags off the walls of a funky-futurist metropolis!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/f94e5feadbba322b37e64016dd083d1a.avif?t=1738003798\" width=615 height=129 /></span><br>Help a cast of <strong><i>hand animated characters</i></strong> fight back against the A.V.A.F by taking on challenges across open level city districts. Compete assorted score based challenges to prove yourself and upgrade your skills!  <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A retro FPS with a new style:</strong> Funky 2D animations and particles clash with an oppressive 3D world, while deep mechanics and fluid movement bring a fresh feel to the genre.<br></li><li><strong>No nonsense gameplay:</strong> Quick switch powers on the fly without worrying about ammo, simple controls mean TAGLINE is easy to learn and difficult to master! <br></li><li><strong>The Sky is the Limit:</strong> Progress through a handcrafted world featuring open playgrounds, each with their own missions and secrets to discover!<br></li><li><strong>5 powerful skills:</strong> Ride explosions, scale buildings, and fly through the air with 5 unique abilities. Each with their own upgrades, dynamic uses, and synergies!<br></li><li><strong>Fill your black book:</strong> Hunt down 100+ unique graffiti designs and chronicle the history of the TAGGERS, a group of street artists lost to time.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/07067e475da74062b7753d86ef766454.poster.avif?t=1738003798\" width=614 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/07067e475da74062b7753d86ef766454.webm?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/07067e475da74062b7753d86ef766454.mp4?t=1738003798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921470/extras/771c476f45f005cfa4252b7f090c1e22.webp?t=1738003798\" width=600 height=57 /></span>"